                    <item name="Size" type_name="gh_single" type_code="5">15</item>
                    <item name="Text" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">This installer will add new libraries to the Ladybug Tools python interpreter which is installed on your computer. 
Specifically, it will:
- Download and add a new ‘Honeybee-PH’ plugin to your Ladybug Tools installation.
- Download and add a new ‘PHX’ plugin to your Ladybug Tools installation.
- Download and add a new library for read/write to excel (XLWings) to your Ladybug Tools installation.
- Download and add new Grasshopper Components to your Grasshopper ‘User Objects’ folder which will then be available
for use in your Grasshopper environment

NOTE: The Honeybee-PH Plugin is currently compatible with Ladybug Tools version v1.8.0 or newer only.</item>
                  </items>
